# Ground Truth Dataset for Classification Evaluation
# Format: One JSON object per line (JSONL)
# Required fields: filename, domain, category, doctype
# Optional fields: vendor, date, subject, notes
#
# Instructions:
# 1. Place test documents in eval/documents/
# 2. Add corresponding entries here with expected classifications
# 3. Run: drover eval --ground-truth eval/ground_truth.jsonl
#
# Example entries (remove or replace with your own):
{"filename": "sample_bank_statement.pdf", "domain": "financial", "category": "banking", "doctype": "statement", "vendor": "Chase", "date": "20250101", "notes": "Monthly checking account statement"}
